#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.30"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.30:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Uruvelavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Paribbājakasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sippinikātīre → sappiniyātīre (bj, pts1) | sippiniyā tīre (s1-3, km) | sippiniyā nadiyā tīre (mr)
msgctxt "an4.30:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā abhiññātā abhiññātā paribbājakā "
"sippinikātīre paribbājakārāme paṭivasanti, seyyathidaṃ annabhāro varadharo "
"sakuludāyī ca paribbājako aññe ca abhiññātā abhiññātā paribbājakā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena sippinikātīraṃ "
"paribbājakārāmo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. Nisajja "
"kho bhagavā te paribbājake etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.30"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārimāni, paribbājakā, dhammapadāni aggaññāni rattaññāni vaṃsaññāni "
"porāṇāni asaṅkiṇṇāni asaṅkiṇṇapubbāni, na saṅkīyanti na saṅkīyissanti, "
"appaṭikuṭṭhāni samaṇehi brāhmaṇehi viññūhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:2.3"
msgid ""
"Anabhijjhā, paribbājakā, dhammapadaṃ aggaññaṃ rattaññaṃ vaṃsaññaṃ porāṇaṃ "
"asaṅkiṇṇaṃ asaṅkiṇṇapubbaṃ, na saṅkīyati na saṅkīyissati, appaṭikuṭṭhaṃ "
"samaṇehi brāhmaṇehi viññūhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:2.4"
msgid ""
"Abyāpādo, paribbājakā, dhammapadaṃ … pe … sammāsati, paribbājakā, "
"dhammapadaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhi, paribbājakā, dhammapadaṃ aggaññaṃ rattaññaṃ "
"vaṃsaññaṃ porāṇaṃ asaṅkiṇṇaṃ asaṅkiṇṇapubbaṃ, na saṅkīyati na saṅkīyissati, "
"appaṭikuṭṭhaṃ samaṇehi brāhmaṇehi viññūhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:2.5"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, paribbājakā, cattāri dhammapadāni aggaññāni rattaññāni vaṃsaññāni "
"porāṇāni asaṅkiṇṇāni asaṅkiṇṇapubbāni, na saṅkīyanti na saṅkīyissanti, "
"appaṭikuṭṭhāni samaṇehi brāhmaṇehi viññūhi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:3.1"
msgid "Yo kho, paribbājakā, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahametaṃ anabhijjhaṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya abhijjhāluṃ kāmesu "
"tibbasārāgaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessāmī’ti, tamahaṃ tattha evaṃ "
"vadeyyaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:3.3"
msgid "‘etu vadatu byāharatu passāmissānubhāvan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:3.4"
msgid ""
"So vata, paribbājakā, anabhijjhaṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya abhijjhāluṃ kāmesu "
"tibbasārāgaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:4.1"
msgid "Yo kho, paribbājakā, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahametaṃ abyāpādaṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya byāpannacittaṃ "
"paduṭṭhamanasaṅkappaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessāmī’ti, tamahaṃ "
"tattha evaṃ vadeyyaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:4.3"
msgid "‘etu vadatu byāharatu passāmissānubhāvan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:4.4"
msgid ""
"So vata, paribbājakā, abyāpādaṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya byāpannacittaṃ "
"paduṭṭhamanasaṅkappaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ "
"vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:5.1"
msgid "Yo kho, paribbājakā, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahametaṃ sammāsatiṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya muṭṭhassatiṃ asampajānaṃ "
"samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessāmī’ti, tamahaṃ tattha evaṃ vadeyyaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:5.3"
msgid "‘etu vadatu byāharatu passāmissānubhāvan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:5.4"
msgid ""
"So vata, paribbājakā, sammāsatiṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya muṭṭhassatiṃ "
"asampajānaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.31"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:6.1"
msgid "Yo kho, paribbājakā, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahametaṃ sammāsamādhiṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya asamāhitaṃ vibbhantacittaṃ "
"samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessāmī’ti, tamahaṃ tattha evaṃ vadeyyaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:6.3"
msgid "‘etu vadatu byāharatu passāmissānubhāvan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:6.4"
msgid ""
"So vata, paribbājakā, sammāsamādhiṃ dhammapadaṃ paccakkhāya asamāhitaṃ "
"vibbhantacittaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā paññāpessatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:7.1"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, paribbājakā, imāni cattāri dhammapadāni garahitabbaṃ paṭikkositabbaṃ "
"maññeyya, tassa diṭṭheva dhamme cattāro sahadhammikā vādānupātā gārayhā "
"ṭhānā āgacchanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:7.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:7.3"
msgid ""
"Anabhijjhañce bhavaṃ dhammapadaṃ garahati paṭikkosati, ye ca hi abhijjhālū "
"kāmesu tibbasārāgā samaṇabrāhmaṇā te bhoto pujjā te bhoto pāsaṃsā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:7.4"
msgid ""
"Abyāpādañce bhavaṃ dhammapadaṃ garahati paṭikkosati, ye ca hi byāpannacittā "
"paduṭṭhamanasaṅkappā samaṇabrāhmaṇā te bhoto pujjā te bhoto pāsaṃsā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:7.5"
msgid ""
"Sammāsatiñce bhavaṃ dhammapadaṃ garahati paṭikkosati, ye ca hi muṭṭhassatī "
"asampajānā samaṇabrāhmaṇā te bhoto pujjā te bhoto pāsaṃsā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:7.6"
msgid ""
"Sammāsamādhiñce bhavaṃ dhammapadaṃ garahati paṭikkosati, ye ca hi asamāhitā "
"vibbhantacittā samaṇabrāhmaṇā te bhoto pujjā te bhoto pāsaṃsā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:8.1"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, paribbājakā, imāni cattāri dhammapadāni garahitabbaṃ paṭikkositabbaṃ "
"maññeyya, tassa diṭṭheva dhamme ime cattāro sahadhammikā vādānupātā gārayhā "
"ṭhānā āgacchanti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: vassabhaññā → vassaṃ bhaññā (pts1) | vassabhiññā (mr)
msgctxt "an4.30:8.2"
msgid ""
"Yepi te paribbājakā ahesuṃ ukkalā vassabhaññā ahetukavādā akiriyavādā "
"natthikavādā, tepi imāni cattāri dhammapadāni na garahitabbaṃ na "
"paṭikkositabbaṃ amaññiṃsu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.30:8.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: Nindābyārosanaupārambhabhayāti → nindābyārosā upārambhabhayati (bj) | … upavādabhayāti (mr)
msgctxt "an4.30:8.4"
msgid "Nindābyārosanaupārambhabhayāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.30:9.1"
msgid "Abyāpanno sadā sato,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.30:9.2"
msgid "ajjhattaṃ susamāhito;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.30:9.3"
msgid "Abhijjhāvinaye sikkhaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.30:9.4"
msgid "appamattoti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.30:9.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.30:9.6"
msgid "Uruvelavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
#. VAR: kāḷako → kāliko (bj) | kāḷiko (pts1) | koḷiko (mr)
msgctxt "an4.30:10.1"
msgid "Dve uruvelā loko kāḷako,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.30:10.2"
msgid "Brahmacariyena pañcamaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.30:10.3"
msgid "Kuhaṃ santuṭṭhi vaṃso ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.30:10.4"
msgid "Dhammapadaṃ paribbājakena cāti."
msgstr ""
